# Description
This plugin provides access to full episodes of The Daily Show, as well as
extended guest interviews.

# Installation
Download the zip file of the desired release from repository page (defined as
<source> in the addon.xml file). Within XBMC, in the "Get Addons" page, select
"install from ZIP" and specify the downloaded zip file.

